make this difficult for me.

78
00:04:12,510 --> 00:04:15,470
Even if the Emperor himself
were here today to take her,

79
00:04:16,040 --> 00:04:18,270
he would have to step over my dead body.

80
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:24,300
If that is the case,
then forgive me for offending you.

81
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,470
Seize them!

82
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,470
After them!

83
00:04:39,560 --> 00:04:40,439
Stop!

84
00:04:40,440 --> 00:04:41,390
Get them!

85
00:04:41,510 --> 00:04:42,620
Stop!

86
00:04:43,360 --> 00:04:44,300
This way!

87
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,540
- Stop!
- Don't run!

88
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,860
This way, hurry!

89
00:04:51,070 --> 00:04:53,030
You go ahead. I'll hold them off.

90
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:53,980
I won't go.

91
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,629
I can't leave you here alone.

92
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:56,709
Listen to me.

93
00:04:56,710 --> 00:04:59,389
General Chen and the South Pacification Lord
are in this together.

94
00:04:59,390 --> 00:05:01,000
They will kill you tonight.

95
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:03,200
Go back to the residence
and hide in the secret chamber.

96
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:05,280
That's the only way we can get
an audience with His Majesty.

97
00:05:05,280 --> 00:05:06,389
I am a prince.

98
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:07,790
They wouldn't dare touch me.

99
00:05:07,950 --> 00:05:09,350
- Go now!
- I won't!

100
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:10,350
- Go!
- No!

